content: Some of these questions are a bit too detailed for now, but I'll try to provide some general info. I usually go to bed around 10:30 PM and fall asleep within 15-20 minutes. I've been reading before bed and trying to relax with a calming tea, which seems to help. I've also cut back on caffeine after 3 PM, which I think has made a difference. However, I still have some nights where I struggle to fall asleep.
